Description: Thob Al Aseel Co (known as: Al Aseel) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Parallel Market” (NOMU) since June 2017. Al Aseel operates within the Consumer Durables & Apparel sector focusing on Apparel, Accessories & Luxury Goods. Al Aseel is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia and was established in February 1989.
